name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Recently, in Jiangsu, a construction worker from Anhui knelt down and kowtowed to his leader, begging him to pay his wages so that he could go home for the New Year. "If you don't pay me, I will fight you to death."

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Currently, Dr. Zheng Minhua has been criticized by many "positive energy" bloggers. Some netizens have also accused him of worshipping foreign things.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
January 23, Shaanxi. Tianlun Yunjing Building owed construction workers wages. Workers stood on the edge of the roof and shouted to the leaders below: We agreed to pay in half a month, but in the end, there is no money. Are you being reasonable? Where is the money?
Not only did the leaders not pay, they also insulted the workers. https://pbs.twimg.com/ext_tw_video_thumb/1882295500495527937/pu/img/6YEHSWYnSPNDDieA.jpg

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
The defendant in the Suzhou Japanese mother and child attack case was sentenced to death.
On the 23rd, the Suzhou Intermediate People's Court sentenced the defendant Zhou Jiasheng (52 years old) who was prosecuted for intentional homicide to death.
The incident occurred at a bus station in Suzhou on June 24, 2024. The Japanese mother and preschool boy were slashed, and the school bus guide, Chinese woman Hu Youping, who tried to stop the defendant, was stabbed to death. https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Gh9w2giakAAqlLg.jpg
